### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/create 接口 => 成功（频率限制规则）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "ruleType": "rate_limit",
  "ruleName": "转链频率限制",
  "ruleKey": "transfer_rate_per_member",
  "ruleValue": "100",
  "timeWindowSeconds": 3600,
  "remark": "每会员每小时最多转链100次",
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/create 接口 => 成功（黑名单规则）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "ruleType": "blacklist",
  "ruleName": "IP黑名单",
  "ruleKey": "ip_blacklist",
  "ruleValue": "192.168.1.100",
  "remark": "异常IP封禁",
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/update 接口 => 成功
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "ruleValue": "200",
  "timeWindowSeconds": 3600,
  "remark": "调整为每小时最多200次",
  "status": 1
}

### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/delete 接口 => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/delete?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/risk/rule/page 接口 => 按规则类型筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/risk/rule/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&ruleType=rate_limit&status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
